room_title: Escape room "Neon Light Diner" by City 13 in Milwaukee
room_description: Ah.. City 13’s only diner in town,  the Neon Light Diner. Back in the day it was the best spot to get some great food with great people. Now it just turned into a new hideout for ‘Steams’ mischief. We know they have more inside there than just some delicious pies. Your crew needs to find out what it is… and take it.
